The standard base-line ‚ÄėUniline‚Äô (‚ÄėINS s 0‚Äô) or ‚Äėaa2u-rectangle‚Äô (‚ÄėINS s
a‚Äô) conversions may be used to convert ASCII art to UNICODE.  The
original ASCII art may be drawn for instance by the ‚Äėartist-mode‚Äô or the
